<p></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-what-does-it-mean-to-be-in-a-cancer-clinical-trial/">Mayo Clinic Q&amp;A: What does it mean to be in a cancer clinical trial?</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
