</ul>



<p>###&nbsp;</p>



<p><strong>About GE HealthCare Technologies Inc.</strong>&nbsp;<br>GE HealthCare is a trusted partner and leading global healthcare solutions provider, innovating medical technology, pharmaceutical diagnostics, and integrated, cloud-first AI-enabled solutions, services and data analytics. It aims to make hospitals and health systems more efficient, clinicians more effective, therapies more precise, and patients healthier and happier. Serving patients and providers for more than 125 years, GE HealthCare is advancing personalized, connected and compassionate care, while simplifying the patient's journey across care pathways. Together, its Imaging, Advanced Visualization Solutions, Patient Care Solutions and Pharmaceutical Diagnostics businesses help improve patient care from screening and diagnosis to therapy and monitoring. GE HealthCare is a $19.7 billion business with approximately 53,000 colleagues working to create a world where healthcare has no limits.&nbsp;</p>



<p>GE HealthCare is proud to be among <a href="https://nam10.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Franking%2Fworlds-most-admired-companies%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7COCE.SupportTeam%40gehealthcare.com%7C9e0a9aa9f24342bda69f08dd4b827cc0%7C9a309606d6ec4188a28a298812b4bbbf%7C0%7C0%7C638749745988740719%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=lT68MWPeh1hpMIhMmUkjm31bg19GOkqd9j%2BKE8yfioQ%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">2025 </a><a href="https://nam10.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Franking%2Fworlds-most-admired-companies%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7COCE.SupportTeam%40gehealthcare.com%7C9e0a9aa9f24342bda69f08dd4b827cc0%7C9a309606d6ec4188a28a298812b4bbbf%7C0%7C0%7C638749745988772649%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=uYkV37NoqWiLDeSwirRYG6rZMKLFs1BfoSol%2F9%2BBv8g%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Fortune</a><a href="https://nam10.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Franking%2Fworlds-most-admired-companies%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7COCE.SupportTeam%40gehealthcare.com%7C9e0a9aa9f24342bda69f08dd4b827cc0%7C9a309606d6ec4188a28a298812b4bbbf%7C0%7C0%7C638749745988787851%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=zjTYbvmfCecIqa5JO6WoaMvkHHKo0o3iwxmHCgMR4q0%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"> World’s Most Admired Companies</a><a href="https://nam10.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Franking%2Fworlds-most-admired-companies%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7COCE.SupportTeam%40gehealthcare.com%7C9e0a9aa9f24342bda69f08dd4b827cc0%7C9a309606d6ec4188a28a298812b4bbbf%7C0%7C0%7C638749745988803321%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8ey